name: Amazon Muscles
description:
It's true, models can already generate muscular people. What this embedding aims to do its reduce changing musculature to a trigger word.

What it's for:

  • Replacing long prompts such as: bodybuilder, thick thighs, muscular thighs, thick arms, muscular arms, thick torso, muscular torso, muscular abs, muscular shoulders, large arms, large thighs, broad shoulders, large torso

  • Making muscular femmes look more feminine. Typically increased prompt words, especially, bodybuilder want to generate masculine features, and put the subject in the gym.

  • Better musculature under clothing.

  • Less extenuated hourglass. Broader torso/abs. For an even bulkier figure, try jujuStyle Lora.

  • More clothes requires more emphasis. See examples for emphasis scaling.

  • Works for anime, and digital painting styles as well.

What it's not for:

  • It can generate masculine subjects, but models typically already do a decent job.

  • Fine-tuning a subject's proportions. Detailed prompting will do better.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: Trained on Deliberate v1.2. 96 images, flipped and cropped. Examples using the trained model, Realistic Vision V1.3, and Rev Animated. See examples for emphasis scaling.
